      "<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  In this exclusive dossier, I am sharing every single thing I’ve ordered so far. I’m not making any promises that I won't place another order (let’s be honest, who can resist?), but this is what is currently winging its way to me! I also have detailed video guides and routines launching on YouTube this week, followed by a full haul and try-on video as soon as the boxes arrive.\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  If any of these formulas catch your eye and you have active cardholder access to shop the sale now, my biggest recommendation is to <strong>check out as quickly as possible</strong>. In this event, the most beautiful shades and gift sets sell out in the blink of an eye.\n</p>",
