      "<h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-theme-text mt-12 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">The Makeup Selection: Viral Icons and Luminous Complexions</h3>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  I also picked up a few different viral makeup pieces. I love the Charlotte Tilbury Flawless Filter line as well as the Westman Atelier Baby Cheeks Blush, and they have a ton of different items included from both of these lines in this year’s Sephora event. Another item that I bought which I’m so excited about is the Dior Lip Glow Oil. It looks so great and is perfect for a hydrated, natural, and effortless look.\n</p>",
      "<div class=\"border border-theme-border my-8 bg-theme-tertiary p-6 rounded-sm\">\n  <h4 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-theme-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border-b border-theme-border pb-2\">Full Makeup Curated List</h4>\n  <ul class=\"list-none space-y-3.5 pl-0\">\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">1. Dior Addict Lip Glow Oil</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/dior-lip-glow-oil-P453814\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">2. Charlotte Tilbury Hollywood Flawless Filter</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/hollywood-flawless-filter-P430419\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">3. Westman Atelier Baby Cheeks Cream Blush Stick</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/baby-cheeks-blush-stick-P433240\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
      "<h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-theme-text mt-12 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">The Haircare & Fragrance Edit: Ultimate Luxury</h3>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  The haircare and fragrance selection is as strong as ever. This is a great time to pick up high-end devices like the Dyson Airwrap or premium fragrance statement bottles like Tom Ford's Lost Cherry at 20% off. Everything is extremely on-trend and there is just so much to choose from. I cannot wait to receive my order!\n</p>",
      "<div class=\"border border-theme-border my-8 bg-theme-tertiary p-6 rounded-sm\">\n  <h4 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-theme-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border-b border-theme-border pb-2\">Full Haircare & Fragrance List</h4>\n  <ul class=\"list-none space-y-3.5 pl-0\">\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">1. Dyson Airwrap Multi-Styler Complete Long</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/dyson-airwrap-multi-styler-complete-long-P500418\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">2. Olaplex No. 3 Hair Perfector Treatment</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/olaplex-no-3-hair-perfector-treatment-P428234\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">3. Tom Ford Lost Cherry Eau de Parfum</span>\n      <a href=\"https://www.sephora.com/product/lost-cherry-P437341\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
      "<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  As I mentioned before, I will be filming my complete skincare and makeup routine hauls on my YouTube channel, so check back if you want to see detailed reviews of these products. I hope you found this guide helpful if you’re shopping the sale and looking for a little bit of inspiration!\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 font-serif italic\">\n  Happy shopping, darlings!\n</p>"
